{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/755830/extras/LA-TrailerGif1-CROPPED_-_Copy.png?t=1605192582\" /><br><br>Lonely Astronaut is a one-button arcade game in which you pilot the corpse of a long-abandoned astronaut floating in a cosmic graveyard. In the process, you might find out something about the human condition. But probably not.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Pilot a Corpse with a Single Button:</strong> With only the ability to thrust the Astronaut's body around with its malfunctioning jetpack, Lonely Astronaut is easy to pick up and <span class=\"bb_strike\">play</span> weep.<br></li><li><strong>Discover Cosmic Truths:</strong> The wonders of space will reveal themselves to you as you play. If only you were alive to see these truths unfold.<br></li><li><strong>Unlock Skulls:</strong> Play dress-up with your corpse because that's healthy, and discover their unique properties.<br></li><li><strong>Feel Existential Dread:</strong> Here's a friendly reminder that you and I are all going to die someday, probably sooner than we'd like to think.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Thanks for Dying!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/755830/0350407be578a0d4cb220bf4c96501e48c3e58b6.jpg"},{"name":"Die Harder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/755830/77b93ca400591f9c91d24eb11c4683c241f87862.jpg"},{"name":"DieAholic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/755830/c23e29f385e47c8fa3f4bddba91e2ca7bda70106.jpg"},{"name":"Planet Cracker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/755830/42220744d1a88eb367b6785c290dd1aabfa23bc8.jpg"},{"name":"Super Nova","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/755830/ed5958bef3bd4037a10a7117f692fb1fcf86e1b8.jpg"},{"name":"Fetus